EMUAID® Delivers Rapid, Natural Relief for Hidradenitis Suppurativa*

 

 

About Hidradenitis Suppurativa Hidradenitis Suppurativa (HS) is a non-contagious, recurrent skin condition or disease. Treatments for HS range from antibiotics to topical ointments. Hidradenitis suppurativa typically manifests as a progression from single boil-like, pus-filled abscesses, or hard sebaceous lumps, to painful, severe, deep-seated and often inflamed clusters of lesions with chronic seepage (suppuration) involving significant scarring. Hidradenitis Suppurativa is often misdiagnosed. It is difficult to treat, and currently there is no known cure.

TREATMENT OF HIDRADENITIS SUPPURATIVA A hidradenitis diagnosis can come based on severe symptoms or more mild symptoms. If the hidradenitis suppurativa disease becomes too severe, treatment could include carbon dioxide laser surgery or other ongoing surgical procedures. Antibiotics taken by mouth can be beneficial, and topical ointments can be another helpful treatment for the disease. Hidradenitis suppurativa patients with severe symptoms are constantly looking for treatment options. A visit to the clinic may not be enough to identify all the drugs and treatment methods necessary, but continual and diligent searching will help those who suffer from hidradenitis suppurativa find treatments that work.
EMUAID® is a revolutionary modern homeopathic topical ointment formulated with powerful natural ingredients and rare growth factor stimulators that work together to alleviate irritation, calm inflammation across a variety of disorders and provide symptomatic relief for damaged and resistant skin conditions, including the symptoms associated with hidradenitis suppurativa .

CALMS INFLAMMATION, ITCHING, PAIN AND DISCOMFORT* Upon application, the powerful natural ingredients in EMUAID® Ointment begin to soothe the skin to calm inflammation, surface pressure, pain and discomfort, regardless of your diagnosis. This makes your skin more comfortable throughout the healing process and also helps the boil to drain. The soothing homeopathic and anti-inflammatory ingredients in EMUAID® Ointment offer relief on contact to calm inflammation and relieve itching, rash and discomfort.* Each of the ingredients in EMUAID® was selected based upon having long histories and clinical support of providing outstanding benefits in skin therapy.

SPEEDS UP HEALING OF DAMAGED SKIN AND IS A PREVENTATIVE SCAR TREATMENT Any time the skin is damaged by a lesion or boil, there is a potential for scarring or permanent blemish. EMUAID® stimulates blood flow to rapidly promote the growth of new healthy skin cells and prevent scar tissue from forming.

MEDICAL GRADE INGREDIENTS TREAT SECONDARY INFECTION EMUAID® naturally fights most harmful bacteria (Staphylococcus and other common bacteria) on the skin to help prevent potential infection.

COMPLETELY SAFE AND PAINLESS – WITH NO SIDE EFFECTS  Unlike other leading products, EMUAID® has no irritating chemicals or reported side effects. It is 100% natural and can be used safely by the entire family. EMUAID® is unsurpassed in its simplicity and power. You cannot develop resistance to EMUAID® - it will work every time you need it and is backed by our 30-Day Guarantee.

 
 




     
