Allison May Rosen

FDA/EMA Communications
Value Communications for Market Access
Executive Communications


Allison May Rosen is an award-winning communicator who specializes in providing strategic communications, content development, and training services for healthcare organizations. Allison brings to 3D more than two decades of experience working in the private and public sectors, including a dozen years at a global healthcare agency where she advised major health companies, trade associations, universities, nonprofits and foundations. A strategic counselor, communications coach and messaging specialist, Allison has earned a reputation for her approachable, creative, hands-on style that delivers results. She excels at helping clients identify their communications strategies, developing messages that matter and improving the performance and confidence of speakers and presenters at all experience levels.


