Price Confirmation & Scheduling
1The details of your quote request will be immediately sent to our pricing department for estimation.
2A nutraceutical specialist expert will call or email to review the details of your price quote.
3Together, we will confirm critical information such as the planned product launch date.
4We will send you a deposit invoice, which you can pay by check or bank wire.















Upon receiving your deposit, we'll start these steps
5Conduct a manufacturing kickoff call to go through the Client Checklist.  Discuss the following topics:
aPackaging & labeling goals
bExpectations & milestones.
cResponsibilities and approval process.
6If your project takes advantage of our design services, we will begin to design the artwork for your label and send over several design compositions for your choosing.
7You will receive the Batch Sheet for approval. (This is the formula that will be saved to the Master Formula Sheet).
8We will send the supplement facts panel for approval.  (Prerequisite #7)
9We'll complete the label design with the approved supplement facts, you must sign off on the label design. (Prerequisite #8)
10Your approved label design will go into print production. (Prerequisite #9)















Once fit into our production schedule, We will give you a 4-week lead time
11Complete a shipment destination form, you will tell us where to ship your product after it is created.
12We will send you the final invoice, covering every service provided.
13Upon confirmation of cleared payment, your supplement order will be shipped within 24 hours.

