Related Markets





Sonic offers packaging for topical, oral, nasal, and other pharmaceutical applications. This industry continues to bridge their science-based formulations with creative delivery systems. Whether it’s on-the-go, a premeasured dose dispensed  to your child at 2 AM, or a regimen of tablets, capsules, or liquids, Sonic continues to partner with the innovators in package materials and filling systems. Our continued focus on tight tolerance dosing, extended shelf life, child resistance and ease of use are a few of our main drivers for determining the ideal packaging system.
Some pharmaceutical packaging options we provide include:

Pharmaceutical sachets
Metal collapsible tubes, including aluminum
Squeeze tubes
Blister packs for tablets, capsules and medications













































